701578f-b.title: Bronx: Parkside Place - Webster Avenue
701578f-b.text:
(1)
Parkside Place (extreme left), west side, at its junction with
Webster Ave. (at East 210th Street), showing excavation work in
progress. The view is in a southerly direction from the Williams-
bridge station (East 210th Street) of the Third Avenue Elevated Line.
May 25, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
(2)
Another view of the same. The frame houses, on the left, face on
the east side of Decatur Ave.
May 25, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS
